synopsis: Shallow and concurrent cloning of git repos
packages: cabal-install
prs: #10254

description: {

- Clone git repositories shallowly, since to build the package from the repository we only need to read the commit specified. The rest of the repo is not needed.
- Clone VCS repositories concurrently, with a maximum of two concurrent tasks at the same time (just like when downloading packages asynchronously)

}

